          },
          "reviewBody": "GKM vidhyashram is one of the best Cbsc school in Tambaram surroundings. It is a child centric school with good infrastructure and facilities. Recomend your kids to enroll in this school to experience the new way of fun filled experimental learning both on school and online classes. Online classes are very well organised and individual care is given to each student.",
