            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "They improved lot from this year after new principal charged. They totally changed like well educated teachers, education system, yoga, karate. Really they are focusing on communication, subjects and sports. Mainly I can see lot of improvements from kids and they are taking care of children.\nMany thanks to GKM management and staff. Way to go!!!",
          "publisher": {
