          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "aarthi ram"
          },
          "datePublished": "2016-05-30",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi. I enrolled my son in GKM school last year in 1st standard and I would say that the school is quite good. The education standard is equal to all the other hyped up schools in Chennai and the teachers i have interacted with seem very kind and knowledgeable. My son has been good at drawing always and the teachers encourage him in this. They also make sure that all kids study well by giving individual attention to the students and understanding their strengths and weaknesses. We live near Tambaram and i has actually searched a lot for quality schools in the area. This school was recommended by my neighbour whose son also studies at GKM. I feel glad that I have made a good choice and that my son's future is in good hands.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
